<bibRefCitation box="[796,1119,1084,1109]" pageId="16" pageNumber="491" refId="ref20841" refString="Mozaffarian, F. &amp; Wilson, M. R. (2016) A checklist of the leafhoppers of Iran (Hemiptera: Auchenorrhyncha: Cicadellidae). Zootaxa, 4062 (1), 1 - 63. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4062.1.1" type="journal article">Mozaffarian &amp; Wilson 2016</bibRefCitation>
